<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on {!HR_Event_Attendance__c.HR_Event_Owner_email__c}</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear {!HR_Event_Attendance__c.Candidate_Name__c},</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I am writing to you in order to confirm the details of your training session with us.</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!HR_Event__c.Date_time_location__c}</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The training session will include various lively group activities and role specific training. As some activities may take place outdoors, please wear appropriate clothing and footwear.</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>What do you need to bring and prepare?</b></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Depending on which option applies to you: staff must bring ALL of the following documents for DBS verification&nbsp;</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>Option 1)</b> You have an existing enhanced DBS dated after April 30th 2013, please bring</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">- Your original DBS certificate with you to training</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>Option 2)</b> You have applied for a DBS through The Challenge, please bring</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">- Your DBS certificate (if you have received this)</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">- All three documents that you uploaded to process your DBS</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">ALL Staff must bring the following ID documents for Right To Work verification&nbsp;</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>Either&nbsp;</b></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">A Passport (with a valid visa where appropriate) or National Identity Card;</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>OR&nbsp;</b></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Original birth certificate AND your National Insurance Card</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">If you do not have documents for either of these options please contact staffing.support@the-challenge.org&nbsp;</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Click on the button below for directions to the training venue.&nbsp;</span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><a href="https://c.na8.content.force.com/email/{!HR_Event__c.Directions__c}" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://www.the-challenge.org/email-newsletters/salesforce-templates-2011/images/get-directions-btn.gif" alt="Get directions" width="290" height="22" border="0"></a></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">We look forward to seeing you!</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Best wishes,</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!HR_Event_Attendance__c.HR_event_Owner__c}</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!HR_Event_Attendance__c.HR_Event_Owner_email__c}</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">NCS with The Challenge</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">CR 1.6.5.3&nbsp;</span></font></div><div><br></div>]]></td>
